Jerry Supiran https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jerry_Supiran 0 Jerry Michael Supiran (born March 21, 1973) is an American former child actor. Supiran is best known for playing Jamie Lawson on the science-fiction sitcom Small Wonder, which aired from 1985 to 1989.
